reviewText: If there was any school on how to parody music you might want to have Weird Al as your Professor and have the art to master it . As I got to listen and watch Downer of the Sister Music Video J. the lead singer for  Apologetix  must have taken his course since he has mastered this parody. If you would like to here the rest of Apologetix music on how J.'s other parodies check out the music here on Amazon.com or go to Apologetix.com for there complete website for more cd's and other item's not found here.
